### 1. 단일 이미지 업로드 (원본)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/images/original
    ?dir=test
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="img3.jpeg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./resources/img3.jpeg
--boundary--


### 2. 여러 이미지 업로드 (원본)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/images/originals
    ?dir=test
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="img1.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./resources/img1.png
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="img2.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./resources/img2.jpg
--boundary--


### 3. 단일 이미지 업로드 (WebP 변환 저장, 크기 지정)
# 예: 모임 상세페이지 썸네일 440x240
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/images/webp
    ?dir=test
    &width=440
    &height=240
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="any-image.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./resources/img1.png
--boundary--


### 4. 단일 이미지 업로드 (여러 크기 WebP 변환 저장)
# 예: 상세(440x240) + 목록(100x100)을 한 번에 생성
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/images/webp/multiple
    ?dir=test&widths=440
    &widths=100
    &heights=240
    &heights=100
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="group-thumbnail.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./resources/img1.png
--boundary--


### 5. 한 개 이미지 삭제
# 업로드 응답에서 받은 key 사용
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/images/one
    ?key=test/20251206141745_0_1f6f3420-0e78-4a5e-b782-93834937c552.webp


### 6. 여러 개 이미지 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/images
    ?keys=test/20251206141808_0_51d58b84-080c-47d2-9ce0-4e50b2e00b63.png
    &keys=test/20251206141808_1_3dea121d-7d39-4e3d-8b02-3dce01a8a929.jpg


### (예외) dir 비어있음 → DIR_REQUIRED
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/images/original?dir=
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="img1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./resources/img1.jpg
--boundary--


### (예외) 디렉토리 경로 traversal → DIR_INVALID_TRAVERSAL
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/images/original?dir=../secret
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="img1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./resources/img1.jpg
--boundary--


### (예외) dir이 / 로 끝남 → DIR_TRAILING_SLASH
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/images/original?dir=test/
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="img1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./resources/img1.jpg
--boundary--

### (예외) dir에 허용되지 않는 문자 포함 → DIR_INVALID_PATTERN
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/images/original?dir=test 이미지
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="img1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./resources/img1.jpg
--boundary--


### (예외) 너무 큰 이미지 업로드 → INVALID_IMAGE_SIZE
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/images/original?dir=test
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="big-image.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./resources/very-big-image.jpg
--boundary--


### (예외) Content-Type이 image/* 가 아님 → UNSUPPORTED_IMAGE_CONTENT_TYPE
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/images/original?dir=test
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="not-image.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./resources/not-image.pdf
--boundary--


### (예외) 확장자는 .xyz, Content-Type 은 image/jpeg → UNSUPPORTED_EXTENSION
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/images/original?dir=test
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="weird.xyz"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./resources/img1.jpg
--boundary--


### (예외) 내용이 이미지가 아님 → INVALID_IMAGE_FORMAT
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/images/webp?dir=test&width=440&height=240
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="fake.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./resources/not-image.txt
--boundary--
